cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper deals with video processing, specifically frame interpolation and super-resolution, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. The proposed training scheme with a multi-scale temporal loss involves regularization, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves analysis of the proposed structure, which could fall under graphics (cs.GR) category.
